snippet.title: War Identity Gameplay Trailer | Invite Only Access Starts October 1st | New PC Multiplayer Game 2020
snippet.description:
Free to play. You can get early access by purchasing a founder pack. Which will give you tokens and other items in the game. Tokens are used to purchase in-game characters, camos, weapons and more.

Join us for some early invite only beta access - https://waridentity.com
